      passage: `<p>Although the greater adjutant appears at scattered sites&mdash;among them the Inner Gulf of Thailand and Manchar Lake in Pakistan&mdash;fully 80 percent of these endangered storks live in Assam, in India. In that state the birds have a champion in wildlife biologist Dr. Purnima Devi Barman, whose conservation efforts _____ through work with local communities and through careful research, aim to bring the adjutant back from near extinction.</p>`,
